blog.title: Chaque fois qu'on se lâche un jour on se retient

summary: People who are saying Disney changed the end of Dark Phoenix because it looked like too much like Captain Marvel are morons....
body:
People who are saying Disney changed the end of Dark Phoenix because it looked like too much like Captain Marvel are morons.

Disney could not interact with any projects involving Fox before the merger that happened in April 2019 or it would be considered as COLLUSION and would have ruined the deal. So, that’s why Disney Marvel and Kevin Feige never even tried to talk about Fantastic Four or the X-Men in general as possibly being part of any phase in the MCU. And Captain Marvel wasn’t even out yet, no one knew how it would be, just because you can’t deal with the fact that Kinberg don’t know how to properly adapt the Dark Phoenix story doesn’t mean everything wrong about it is a Disney problem. Fox should have left that movie the way it was and let it be dropped last year. 

People act like we never had a precedent of this with Fox, do you remember the last Fantastic Four movie was literally butchered with badly used reshoots. 

I truly have enough with people trying to shit on Captain Marvel every five seconds for everything wrong in the world. What a bunch of assholes.
